      "instruction": "<p>Set the <strong>creamy Tenderstem &amp; kale gnocchi</strong> in the centre of the table, ready to share</p>\n<p>Top with the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p>\n<p>Garnish with the<strong> lemon wedges</strong> (squeeze them over to taste!) and let everyone dig in</p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
